{
  "stem": "8784.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We would also witness hangings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hangings were going on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The movie does not show any hangings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The movie does not show hangings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there were hangings going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When those hangings were going on, all the inmates had to file by and, and look closely as to what hung people looked like.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember some of my friends-- two, two brothers-- that were hung, brothers by the name of Spielman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I actually went to cheder together with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were hung.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Supposedly, rumor had it that they were trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But, of course, all these things might have not been true at all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we would continue our work at Oskar Schindler's factory until sometime in 1943.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Toward the end of 1943, to the best of my knowledge, an order came out, the Jews will no longer be able to work outside of a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, therefore, we were stopped from going to Oskar Schindler's work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to work in the camp again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, once again, I became a full inmate of the, of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was staying there and working there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but unbeknown to me at that time again, Schindler, Schindler was told about it that he can no longer have people walking out of the concentration camp to work for him.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would have to give up his workforce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Schindler, at that time, after witnessing the liquidation of the ghetto as we know now from readings and the movie-- we know that after Schindler has witnessed the brutalities of his fellow Germans that they were committing against the Jews, he was no longer a loyal German.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he began to scheme his own future, his future.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
